Package org.drools.conflict

Class Summary
AbstractConflictResolver Convenience base class for ConflictResolvers.
ComplexityConflictResolver ConflictResolver that uses the numConditions of rules to resolve conflict.
CompositeConflictResolver Strategy for resolving conflicts amongst multiple rules.
DepthConflictResolver  
FifoConflictResolver ConflictResolver that orders rules on a First-In-First-Out basis.
LifoConflictResolver ConflictResolver that orders rules on a Last-In-First-Out basis.
LoadOrderConflictResolver ConflictResolver that uses the loadOrder of rules to resolve conflict.
RandomConflictResolver ConflictResolver that uses the semi-random order of rules to resolve conflict.
RecencyConflictResolver ConflictResolver that uses the mostRecentFactTimeStamp of rules to resolve conflict.
SalienceConflictResolver ConflictResolver that uses the salience of rules to resolve conflict.
SimplicityConflictResolver ConflictResolver that uses the numConditions of rules to resolve conflict.
TotalRecencyConflictResolver A conflict resolver that compares the total recency of a tuple when determining firing order.
